ChatApp
Description
ChatApp is an iOS chat application built using Swift and Stream ChatUI. The app allows users to sign up, create channels, and chat with other users in real-time.

Installation
Clone the repository:
shell

$ git clone https://github.com/yourusername/chatapp.git
Install dependencies using CocoaPods:
shell

$ cd chatapp
$ pod install
Open ChatApp.xcworkspace in Xcode.
Build and run the app.

Usage
Sign up for a new account or log in with an existing one.
Create a new channel or join an existing one.
Start chatting with other users in real-time.

Features
User authentication and authorization.
Real-time chat using Stream ChatUI.
Creating and joining channels.
Sending and receiving messages.
Editing and deleting messages.


